Package com.opengamma.strata.product.index

Entity objects describing contracts based on rate indices.

A future is an exchange traded contract that involves buying an underlying asset at a price agreed today for delivery at a date in the future.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RateIndexSecurity
    An instrument representing a security associated with a rate index.
